" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-cuc-chup-anh-chan-dung.html\/#Diem_quan_trong_nhat_buc_hinh_trong_bo_cuc_chup_anh_chan_dung\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh trong b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung\">\u0110i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh trong b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-cuc-chup-anh-chan-dung.html\/#Cac_kieu_bo_cuc_chup_anh_chan_dung_pho_bien\" title=\"C\u00e1c ki\u1ec3u b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn\">C\u00e1c ki\u1ec3u b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-cuc-chup-anh-chan-dung.html\/#Bo_cuc_giua_tam_buc_anh\" title=\"B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c gi\u1eefa t\u00e2m b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh\u00a0\">B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c gi\u1eefa t\u00e2m b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-cuc-chup-anh-chan-dung.html\/#Bo_cuc_13\" title=\"B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c 1\/3\">B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c 1\/3<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-cuc-chup-anh-chan-dung.html\/#Bo_cuc_theo_duong_thang\" title=\"B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c theo \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng\">B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c theo \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-cuc-chup-anh-chan-dung.html\/#Bo_cuc_theo_khuon_mau_lap_lai\" title=\"B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c theo khu\u00f4n m\u1eabu l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i\">B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c theo khu\u00f4n m\u1eabu l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-cuc-chup-anh-chan-dung.html\/#Bo_cuc_chup_anh_chan_dung_dang_khung\" title=\"B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung d\u1ea1ng khung\">B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung d\u1ea1ng khung<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>Ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111a s\u1ed1 trong ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1ea3i qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u1edbi l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh. B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7m m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc m\u00e1y t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 m\u1eabu xinh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y trong \u0111\u1eddi b\u1ea1n. Sau khi ch\u1ee5p xong b\u1ea1n v\u00f2 \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ee9t tai khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 tr\u0103m t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb h\u01b0! Gi\u1edd bi\u1ebft l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u00e2y? \u0110\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f3 n\u00e0y, h\u00e3y b\u1ecf ch\u00fat th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u01b0\u1edbt qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 <strong>b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung<\/strong> d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e9.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Diem_quan_trong_nhat_buc_hinh_trong_bo_cuc_chup_anh_chan_dung\"><\/span><strong>\u0110i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh trong b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n kinh nghi\u1ec7m, h\u1ecd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u1eadc th\u1ea7y trong<strong> b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung<\/strong>, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng quy t\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 s\u00e1ng t\u00e1c ra nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t.<\/p>\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi v\u00e0o ngh\u1ec1 nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang ta, c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1eabn l\u00e0 n\u00ean tu\u00e2n theo nh\u1eefng quy t\u1eafc ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m trong s\u00e1ch gi\u00e1o khoa t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m n\u0103m qua. Trong m\u1ed7i b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m m\u00e0 khi l\u01b0\u1edbt qua, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta s\u1ebd nh\u00ecn th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9751\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/b31c6330591453953a95d6329a47e7a6.jpg\" alt=\"b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung\" width=\"850\" height=\"1135\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/b31c6330591453953a95d6329a47e7a6.jpg 599w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/b31c6330591453953a95d6329a47e7a6-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Trong <strong>\u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung<\/strong>, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0110\u00d4I M\u1eaeT, nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ebft hoa r\u1eb1ng: \u0110\u00d4I M\u1eaeT l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong ch\u1ee5p ch\u00e2n dung! V\u00ec v\u1eady, trong m\u1ecdi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea5y n\u00e9t v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f4i m\u1eaft, \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u00f4i m\u1eaft v\u00e0o trung t\u00e2m b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f4i m\u1eaft b\u1ecb m\u1edd th\u00ec c\u1ea3 t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh s\u1ebd m\u1edd t\u1ecbt theo, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i n\u00e9t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cac_kieu_bo_cuc_chup_anh_chan_dung_pho_bien\"><\/span><strong>C\u00e1c ki\u1ec3u b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Bo_cuc_giua_tam_buc_anh\"><\/span><strong>B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c gi\u1eefa t\u00e2m b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t an to\u00e0n. B\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb7t ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eabu v\u00e0o \u0111\u00fang t\u00e2m b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh, v\u00e0 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf ki\u1ec3u g\u00ec b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u1ecb sai. B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c gi\u1eefa t\u00e2m\u00a0nhi\u1ec1u khi r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, v\u00ed d\u1ee5 trong ch\u1ee5p k\u1ef7 y\u1ebfu t\u1eeb 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1edf l\u00ean ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Xem th\u00eam:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/ky-thuat-chup-anh-phoi-sang.html\/\">K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ph\u01a1i s\u00e1ng<\/a><\/strong><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/y-tuong-chup-anh-chan-dung-doc-dao.html\/\"><strong>\u00dd t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o<\/strong><\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9736\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/tao-dang-chup-anh-cuoi-trong-studio-luu-y.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00e1c ki\u1ec3u ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh\" width=\"850\" height=\"1070\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/tao-dang-chup-anh-cuoi-trong-studio-luu-y.jpg 650w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/tao-dang-chup-anh-cuoi-trong-studio-luu-y-238x300.jpg 238w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Bo_cuc_13\"><\/span><strong>B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c 1\/3<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><strong>B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung<\/strong> 1\/3 l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n kh\u00e1c. Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc l\u00e0 chia \u1ea3nh th\u00e0nh 9 ph\u1ea7n b\u1eb1ng nhau nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi. C\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m giao nhau l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng, c\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng chia 1\/3 \u1ea3nh l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng quan tr\u1ecdng. M\u1eaft ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd b\u1ecb thu h\u00fat v\u00e0o c\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft c\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, v\u00ed d\u1ee5 \u0111\u00f4i m\u1eaft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eabu, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2n tr\u1eddi&#8230;<\/p>\n<p>B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c 1\/3 gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd khi xem phim, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u1edf 1\/3 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh gi\u1eefa.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9719\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/t_an136_12_4_2018_22_55_37_498-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00e1ch ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung\" width=\"850\" height=\"637\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/t_an136_12_4_2018_22_55_37_498-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/t_an136_12_4_2018_22_55_37_498-1024x767.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/t_an136_12_4_2018_22_55_37_498-768x575.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/t_an136_12_4_2018_22_55_37_498.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Bo_cuc_theo_duong_thang\"><\/span><strong>B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c theo \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>M\u1eaft ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u00f5i theo \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. V\u00ec v\u1eady ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem t\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh. Ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t trong ch\u00e2n dung, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecm nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 l\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, h\u00e0ng c\u00e2y, thanh ray \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eaft&#8230; v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eabu tr\u00ean c\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng \u0111\u00f3.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9718\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/pho-sach-ha-noi-300x292.jpg\" alt=\"b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c theo \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng\" width=\"850\" height=\"826\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/pho-sach-ha-noi-300x292.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/pho-sach-ha-noi-1024x995.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/pho-sach-ha-noi-768x746.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/pho-sach-ha-noi.jpg 1242w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Bo_cuc_theo_khuon_mau_lap_lai\"><\/span><strong>B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c theo khu\u00f4n m\u1eabu l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>M\u1eaft ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng b\u1ecb cu\u1ed1n h\u00fat t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng khu\u00f4n m\u1eabu l\u1eb7p \u0111i l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i. V\u00ec v\u1eady nh\u1eefng khung c\u1ea3nh l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh n\u1ec1n th\u00fa v\u1ecb cho b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, v\u00ed d\u1ee5 c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed3ng hoa, l\u00e1 c\u00e2y,&#8230;<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8759\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/cac-dia-diem-chup-anh-dep-o-ha-noi-17-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00e1c d\u00e1ng ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh\" width=\"850\" height=\"1133\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/cac-dia-diem-chup-anh-dep-o-ha-noi-17-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/cac-dia-diem-chup-anh-dep-o-ha-noi-17-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/cac-dia-diem-chup-anh-dep-o-ha-noi-17-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/cac-dia-diem-chup-anh-dep-o-ha-noi-17.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Bo_cuc_chup_anh_chan_dung_dang_khung\"><\/span><strong>B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung d\u1ea1ng khung<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc khung t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 \u00f4 c\u1eeda s\u1ed5, c\u00e2y c\u1ed1i, ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u1ee9 g\u00ec l\u00e0m th\u00e0nh khung xung quanh ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eabu c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8189\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chup-anh-cuoi-tai-nha-trang.jpg4_-300x230.jpg\" alt=\"b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung\" width=\"850\" height=\"652\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chup-anh-cuoi-tai-nha-trang.jpg4_-300x230.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chup-anh-cuoi-tai-nha-trang.jpg4_-1024x786.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chup-anh-cuoi-tai-nha-trang.jpg4_-768x590.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chup-anh-cuoi-tai-nha-trang.jpg4_.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n trong <strong>b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n dung<\/strong> v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng. Khi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c quy t\u1eafc n\u00e0y v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. Sau n\u00e0y, khi \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ea7n th\u1ee5c, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 &#8220;phi\u00eau&#8221; v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o t\u00f9y th\u00edch.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111a s\u1ed1 trong ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1ea3i qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u1edbi l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh. B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7m m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc m\u00e1y t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 m\u1eabu xinh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y trong \u0111\u1eddi b\u1ea1n. Sau khi ch\u1ee5p xong b\u1ea1n v\u00f2 \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ee9t tai khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 tr\u0103m t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb h\u01b0! Gi\u1edd bi\u1ebft&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":9858,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[94,63],"tags":[571,96],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>B\u1ed1 C\u1ee5c Ch\u1ee5p \u1ea2nh Ch\u00e2n Dung C\u01a1 B\u1ea3n Cho Ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1edbi B\u1eaft \u0110\u1ea7u<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 d\